reviewText: Very good condition. Stories are not completely accurate with the Bible but they get the general point across to children.
It's totally my fault, but I never realized this was a VHS.  It should have been more prominent in the title.
Superbook has great Bible stories. My daughter, 28, and I love to watch this series.

My Children are young adults and teenages and they love the superbook stories they found them an exciting way to learn the bible for them the stories came alive, now my son wants his son to have the same experience he did from them.
